ent-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="玛丽·沃勒斯 (Mary Wallopers)、江湖骗子 (The Charlatans) 和未来领袖 (The Futureheads)" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mary-Wallopers-Charlatans-Futureheads@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mary-Wallopers-Charlatans-Futureheads@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mary-Wallopers-Charlatans-Futureheads@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mary-Wallopers-Charlatans-Futureheads@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mary-Wallopers-Charlatans-Futureheads@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Mary-Wallopers-Charlatans-Futureheads@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-libertines">浪子乐队 (The Libertines)</a>透露了哪些艺术家将参加他们即将举行的布莱顿演出，其中包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-charlatans">The Charlatans</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-mary-wallopers">The Mary Wallopers</a>等。请在下面查找门票详细信息。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-interview-pete-doherty-carl-barat-all-quiet-eastern-esplanade-3517826"><b>The Libertines 谈论干净和联系：“我们只是想在当下写出优美的歌曲”</b></a></strong></li></ul><p>就在这一消息发布的一天前，独立重量级人物<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-libertines-announce-huge-summer-2024-show-at-brighton-beach-buy-tickets-3584417">宣布了他们在 On The Beach 2024 上的头条新闻</a>。该演出与<em>Radio X</em>联合举办，定于 7 月 28 日举行，是布莱顿海滩两个周末演出的一部分； <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-kooks">Kooks 队</a>已经确定将在之前的周末（7 月 21 日，星期日）进行比赛。</p><p> “嗯，你好，布莱顿海滩！”他们在标题中写道，分享了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/pete-doherty">皮特·多尔蒂</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/carl-barat">卡尔·巴拉特</a>欣赏当地风景的片段，背景播放着“不要回头看太阳”。</p><p>现在，在 The Charlatans 的支持下，将于 7 月 28 日登台的其余艺术家已经分享完毕。由蒂姆·伯吉斯 (Tim Burgess) 领衔的现场表演将继他们<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-charlatans-announce-2023-uk-winter-tour-3452270">去年冬天最近的英国巡演</a>之后，并将在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/johnny-marr-and-the-charlatans-announce-huge-uk-2024-co-headline-outdoor-shows-3557403">他们与约翰尼·马尔 (Johnny Marr) 共同主持的大型英国演出</a>之后到来。</p><p>继去年夏天在英国各地举办音乐节之后，爱尔兰民谣摇滚乐队 The Mary Wallopers 也被列入该名单，并考虑到他们十月份的第二张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/en_au/news/music/the-mary-wallopers-interview-single-wexford-uk-tour-dates-buy-tickets-3469634">“Irish Rock &amp; Roll”</a> 。</p><p>其余阵容包括伦敦乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-big-moon">The Big Moon</a> ，他们于 2022 年分享了他们的第三张专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/the-big-moon-here-is-everything-review-3328102">《Here Is Everything》</a> ；英国后朋克乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/the-futureheads">The Futureheads</a> ，他们将庆祝他们成立 10 周年。与当地鞋迷和英伦流行乐队<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappaqua-wrestling">Chappaqua Wrestling</a>合作的首张专辑。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/C3GRajUs8MK/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" v